description: Sprawling hotel offering contemporary rooms, breakfast, a thermal pool & spa access.
address: 2A Av. Dr Ernest Feltgen, 5635 Mondorf-les-Bains, Luxembourg
hotelDescription:
Spread across 45 hectares of green space, this contemporary hotel is an 8-minute walk from Casino 2000, and 11 km from Schloss Thorn castle and winery.
 Streamlined, modern rooms offer stylish decor and balconies, plus flat-screen TVs, minibars and Wi-Fi. Suites add sitting areas and expanded bar services, and some have pull-out sofas.
 A breakfast buffet is available. Amenities include 3 restaurants and a cocktail bar. There's also a wellness area with a thermal pool and a fitness center, plus treatments at the spa. Minimum-stay rules may apply.

title: Mercure Luxembourg Kikuoka Golf and Spa
description: Refined hotel offering an 18-hole golf course, a restaurant & a bar, plus a spa with an indoor pool.
hotelDescription:
Set on lush grounds, this genteel hotel is 7 km from Musée et Maison du Vin and 9 km from Munsbach Castle.
 Understated rooms and suites offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and minifridges, as well as Nespresso machines. Some have sitting areas and/or sofabeds.
 Parking is complimentary. Other amenities consist of a restaurant, an 18-hole golf course and a bar, plus a terrace, a garden, and meeting and event space. There's also a spa with an exercise room, a hammam and a heated indoor pool, as well as a sauna and a hot tub. Breakfast and bike rentals are available.
